Section · Conferences


●Dissemination & community

The Virtual Biophysical Lab is presented and discussed at selected scientific meetings and mission-oriented workshops. These venues are used to share methodological advances, prototype tools, and reproducible examples related to radiative transfer modelling, imaging spectroscopy, and EO-based plant trait retrieval. {.section-intro}

